---
title: Quick Beef & Tabbouleh-Style Salad  with Couscous & Yoghurt
description: Take your taste buds on a trip to the Middle East with this colourful tabbouleh-style salad! Juicy, spiced beef meets a fresh, zesty salad that’s bursting with herbs, tomatoes, and a hint of citrus. Topped with a dollop of creamy Greek-style yoghurt and a sprinkle of parsley, this vibrant, flavour-packed bowl will be too good to put down.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
